OL,3,COne in six older people in Wales live
OL,4,Cin poverty, report reveals
OL,6,FOne in six older people in Wales are
OL,7,Fliving in poverty, a report reveals.
OL,9,FThe report by the Older People's
OL,10,FCommissioner also shows that this
OL,11,Fnumber increases to one in four for
OL,12,Fwomen living alone, while it is
OL,13,Festimated that nearly half of Black,
OL,14,FAsian and Minority Ethnic households
OL,15,Fin Wales are affected.
OL,17,FThe Older People's Commissioner said
OL,18,Fthe Welsh and UK Governments need to
OL,19,Fdeliver a range of action to ensure
OL,20,Folder people living in poverty are
OL,21,Fbetter supported.
