OL,3,COne in six older people in Wales live
OL,4,Cin poverty, report reveals
OL,6,FIn a statement, the Welsh Government
OL,7,Fsaid its "determined" to do all it can
OL,8,Fto prevent people from going into
OL,9,Fpoverty.
OL,11,FThe report highlights that many more
OL,12,Folder people are struggling due to the
OL,13,Fimpact of the cost-of-living crisis
OL,14,Fand rapidly rising prices, which have
OL,15,Fparticularly affected people living on
OL,16,Ffixed incomes.
OL,18,FIt describes the choices many older
OL,19,Fpeople are forced to make in their
OL,20,Feveryday lives, including going
OL,21,Fwithout heating or skipping meals.
