OL,3,COne in six older people in Wales live
OL,4,Cin poverty, report reveals
OL,6,FDiscussing the report, Older People's
OL,7,FCommissioner for Wales, Rhian Bowen-
OL,8,FDavies, said: "As the weather turns
OL,9,Fcolder, older people across Wales will
OL,10,Ffind themselves worrying about how
OL,11,Fthey will be able to pay the bills,
OL,12,Fand many may soon be forced to choose
OL,13,Fbetween 'heating or eating', putting
OL,14,Ftheir health and well-being at serious
OL,15,Frisk, something that sadly now seems
OL,16,Fto have become normalised within
OL,17,Fsociety.
