OL,4,Cin poverty, report reveals
OL,6,F"Investing in tackling poverty could
OL,7,Funlock tens of millions of pounds that
OL,8,Fcould be used to improve our public
OL,9,Fservices and communities here in Wales.
OL,11,F"So in the immediate term, we need to
OL,12,Fsee greater support for older people
OL,13,Fwho are living in poverty or
OL,14,Fstruggling financially, including
OL,15,Fthose who do not currently qualify for
OL,16,Fother forms of support.
